Class SessionManager

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Thread
      SessionManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable, ShutdownInterface
public class SessionManager
extends java.lang.Thread
implements ShutdownInterface

Manages all the sessions that this program participates in. If the object returned from getActiveSessions() is modified, correctness not guaranteed.
